comments.body:
Thanks [~giovanni.fumarola] for reviewing the patch. 
{quote}You have this instruction {{int threadPoolSize = Math.max(poolSize, 10);}} instead of 10 you should have {{SLSConfiguration.RUNNER_POOL_SIZE_DEFAULT;}}
{quote}
Will fix it.
{quote}{{executorService.awaitTermination(1, TimeUnit.HOURS);}} I think the awaiting time is too long. How did you come up with this value?
{quote}
I tried with 5000 nodes and it was taking around similar time without this fix. I will reduce it to 10 minutes with this fix.

